DECLARE_TASKLET_DISABLE

Key APIs
-Tasklet_init Invoked inside probe
-Tasklet_Schedule Invoked inside IRQ

Soft IrQ
11 types
Timer,Net_Rx,Net_Tx,etc 

Workqueues
-Non atomic
-Kernel Context






